打电话也没用。<br /><br />今天因果报应我的红米 k40 也坏了，正取着快递，翻短信的收件码，突然就黑屏了，开机键没反应，插电源也没反应。<br /><br />我以为我很了解手机能避过这一遭，当年刷机卡 fastboot 我直接跑到小米售后说 9008 给我重刷一下，记得勾上刷完重启手机。很是潇洒呀，5 分钟不到就解决战斗了，一毛钱没收我。<br /><br />都成我这种钉子户，小米早破产了，我现在极度怀疑这些手机厂商在各种机型上没有下限的往下探，制造手机报废计划。<br /><br />初步怀疑 cpu 虚焊。过两天去售后看看，再回帖。", "last_modified": 1726145360, "replies": 158, "id": 1072408}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6302, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1510, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 683522, "username": "aaxaax", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aaxaax", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_mini.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_normal.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_large.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c84c/a26e/683522_xlarge.png?m=1723084531", "created": 1712120057, "last_modified": 1723084531}, "last_reply_by": "idou", "last_touched": 1726212618, "title": "中秋三天大家什么安排？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1072484", "created": 1726189323, "deleted": 0, "content": "我准备大门不出二门不迈，在家二周目黑神话悟空，你们嘞？", "content_rendered": "<p>我准备大门不出二门不迈，在家二周目黑神话悟空，你们嘞？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1726189323, "replies": 143, "id": 1072484}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com